feed.title: Netherlands House
feed.description:
Those are the readings of my house in Delft,  Netherlands!
Winter is coming and I would like to take control of the temperature as now I have to pay for the gas. 
My Room is quite cold and humid so I decided to take actions and I decided to go my way,  digital 10101000111101010...
First, data is collected from a temperature and Humidity sensor, a DHT11 using an Arduino UNO board.
The code is almost the example code provided for the sensor, as it works perfect.
I picked up the  Pachube_in_out code and added some modification to include my sensor readings. 
The Ethernet shield is later used to feed Pachube at intervals of 1minute or so.


Why do I do this? Because its really fun and I dont like cold!

=p
